CM_ SG_ 315 GlobalRealTimeRaw_PMZ "The raw Global Real Time value calculated in the BCM. 
This value is used by the Vehicle Information Parameters master to populate the Global Real Time value in the  Vehicle Information Parameters signal.
All nodes except the Vehicle Information Parameters master should use the Global Real Time from the Vehicle Information Parameters signal, they must NOT subscribe to this signal.
If there is no value available on Global real time, the value shall be 0xFFFFFFFF.";
