CM_ SG_ 114 Timed12VLoadEnergyLeft "This will be used to educate the customer that selected loads impact their range.

This is the total remaining energy consumption of the customer actived 'timed' 12V loads controlled by the HVAC module, not considering whether they are currently load-managed off.

Stealth deployment is not shown here, auto operation is.

e.g. If the user switches on the heated front screen and this will be on for 3 minutes, then the signal should jump up to the value of [Amps current consumption*13.5V*0.05 hours] and begin to count down, such that its remaining energy crosses 0 after 3 minutes has elapsed.";
