0 - Undefined
1 - Swedish
2 - Danish
3 - Finnish
4 - English
5 - German
6 - Dutch
7 - French
8 - Italian
9 - Spanish
10 - Portuguese
11 - English (US)
12 - French (Canadian)
13 - Japanese (Katakana)
14 - Portuguese (Brazil)
15 - English with number codes
16 - Hungarian
17 - Turkish
18 - Russian
19 - Polish
20 - Czech
21 - Norwegian
22 - Latin Spanish
23 - English (Australian)
24 - Thai
25 - Ford Asia Pacific English
26 - Chinese (Simplified)
27 - Taiwanese
28 - Chinese (Traditional)
29 - Flemish
30 - Bulgarian
31 - Estonian
32 - Greek
33 - Latvian
34 - Lithuanian
35 - Romanian
36 - Slovakian
37 - Slovene
38 - Korean
39 - Croatian
40 - Malaysian
41 - Arabic
42 - Chinese_Mandarin
43 - Chinese_Wu
44 - Chinese_Cantonese
45 - 62 Reserved
63 - Error (default = English)";
