CM_ SG_ 13 WheelTorqTgtWoIntF "This is the 'long term' target front wheels torque. This includes driver demand (accelerator pedal) , vehicle motion control functions (i.e. cruise, ACC, ASL, vehicle speed limitation), and long term torque limitations  & offsets (i.e. driveline protection)
This request excludes short term interventions (i.e. Traction Control, Shift Energy Management).
Inertial terms are not included / compensated for (steady state speed is assumed).";
CM_ SG_ 13 WheelTorqTgtWoIntR "This is the 'long term' target rear wheels torque. This includes driver demand (accelerator pedal) , vehicle motion control functions (i.e. cruise, ACC, ASL, vehicle speed limitation), and long term torque limitations  & offsets (i.e. driveline protection)
This request excludes short term interventions (i.e. Traction Control, Shift Energy Management).
Inertial terms are not included / compensated for (steady state speed is assumed).";
